WiFlyRSSIGraph.ino
===========

WiFlyRSSIGraph.ino is an example application of the WiFly module with a graphical LCD.  It displays the WiFly's network connection strength (RSSI) plotted as a function of time.

The project requires the following hardware:

- [Arduino FIO](http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B005K0O1PA/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&camp=1789&creative=390957&creativeASIN=B005K0O1PA&linkCode=as2&tag=semifluidcom-20&linkId=I2HIBY7CN3WQ7QQD)
- [RN-XV WiFly module](http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B007R9U4VM/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&camp=1789&creative=390957&creativeASIN=B007R9U4VM&linkCode=as2&tag=semifluidcom-20&linkId=GHYDRHL4FKNQPCZ6)
- [Mini12864 Graphic LCD module](http://www.dx.com/p/mini12864-blue-backlight-dots-graphic-lcd-display-module-red-153821?Utm_rid=62305252&Utm_source=affiliate)

The project also requires that the [WiFlyHQ](https://github.com/harlequin-tech/WiFlyHQ) library is installed.